flowchart TD
  A([Start]) --> B[User types message in UI]
  B --> C[Frontend sends POST /chat]
  C --> D[Flask receives request]
  D --> E[ChatService.generate_reply]

  E --> F{Message empty?}
  F -- Yes --> G[Return default prompt]
  F -- No --> H{Emotions enabled?}
  H -- Yes --> I[EmotionClassifier predicts emotions]
  H -- No --> J[Skip emotions]

  I --> K[Detect intent + topic]
  J --> K

  K --> L{Use KB and intent is info/symptom?}
  L -- Yes --> M[KB Retriever search]
  M --> N[Format KB answer]
  N --> O{KB answer exists?}
  O -- Yes --> P[Compose KB-based reply]
  O -- No --> Q[Compose fallback question]

  L -- No --> R[Compose support/calming reply]

  P --> S[Apply safety constraints]
  Q --> S
  R --> S
  G --> S

  S --> T[Return JSON response]
  T --> U[Frontend displays reply]
  U --> V([End])
